Package: neschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Nebraska School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Nebraska Department of
    Education. Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from NDE's
    public data reports and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
    Supports data from 2016 to present with demographic breakdowns by grade,
    race, and gender.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
